<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.4.10">
<l>pūmāṇcēr karuṅkuḻalār pōlnaṭantu vayalniṉṟa peṭaiyō ṭaṉṉam</l>
<l>tēmāvi ṉiṉṉiḻalil kaṇṭuyilun taṇcēṟai yammāṉ ṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>vāmāṉtērp parakālaṉ kalikaṉṟi yolimālai koṇṭu toṇṭīr</l>
<l>tūmāṇcēr poṉṉaṭimēl cūṭṭumiṉṉum tuṇaikkaiyāl</l>
<l>toḻutu niṉṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Devotees, taking this garland of song on the lord of cool Cēṟai,</l>
<l rend="indent">where a swan which had tarried with its mate in the fields,</l>
<l>Walking like [girls] whose dark curls have glorious flowers,</l>
<l rend="indent">[then] rests its eyes in the pleasant shade of a ripe mango tree,</l>
<l>By Kalikaṉṟi, Parakālaṉ whose chariot has leaping steeds,</l>
<l>And worshipping continually with your joined hands,</l>
<l rend="indent">crown [yourself] with the lord’s feet of glorious pure gold.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
